ernment%20circular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20exporters%2C%20mainly%20from%20the%20apparel%20sector%2C%20had%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20withdraw%20this%20facility%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20enabled%20smooth%20trade%20flows%20for%20Bangladesh's%20exports%20to%20countries%20like%20Bhutan%2C%20Nepal%2C%20and%20Myanmar.%20It%20was%20provided%20by%20India%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20rescind...%20circular...%20dated%20June%2029%2C%202020%2C%20as%20amended%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20Cargo%20already%20entered%20into%20India%20may%20be%20allowed%20to%20exit%20the%20Indian%20territory%20as%20per%20the%20procedure%20given%20in%20that%20circular%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Indirect%20Taxes%20and%20Customs'%20circular%2C%20dated%20April%208%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US%20imposed%20sweeping%20tariffs%20against%20a%20number%20of%20countries%2C%20including%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20circular%20allowed%20transshipment%20of%20export%20cargo%20from%20Bangladesh%20to%20third%20countries%20using%20Indian%20land%20customs%20stations%20(LCSs)%20en%20route%20to%20Indian%20ports%20and%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F1re1b3v8_india-cargo-mumbai-generic-reuters_625x300_15_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trade%20experts%2C%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20many%20Indian%20exporting%20sectors%20like%20apparel%2C%20footwear%2C%20and%20gems%20and%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20a%20big%20competitor%20of%20India%20in%20the%20textile%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20will%20have%20more%20air%20capacity%20for%20our%20cargo.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20exporters%20have%20complained%20about%20lesser%20space%20due%20to%20the%20transhipment%20facility%20given%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Export%20Organisations%20(FIEO)%20Director%20General%20Ajay%20Sahai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparel%20exporters'%20body%20AEPC%20had%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20suspend%20this%20order%2C%20which%20allowed%20trans-shipment%20of%20Bangladesh%20export%20cargo%20to%20third%20countries%20through%20the%20Delhi%20air%20cargo%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAEPC%20chairman%20Sudhir%20Sekhri%20said%2020-30%20loaded%20trucks%20arrive%20in%20Delhi%20every%20day%2C%20which%20slows%20down%20the%20smooth%20movement%20of%20cargo%2C%20and%20airlines%20are%20taking%20undue%20advantage%20of%20this.%20This%20leads%20to%20an%20excessive%20increase%20in%20air%20freight%20rates%2C%20delay%20in%20handling%20and%20processing%20of%20export%20cargo%2C%20and%20severe%20congestion%20at%20the%20cargo%20terminal%20at%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20Delhi%2C%20resulting%20in%20exports%20of%20Indian%20apparel%20through%20the%20Delhi%20air%20cargo%20complex%20becoming%20uncompetitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20help%20in%20rationalization%20of%20freight%20rates%20resulting%20in%20less%20transportation%20cost%20to%20the%20Indian%20exporters%20besides%20decongesting%20the%20airports%20leading%20to%20the%20shorter%20transit%20time%20to%20ship%20the%20goods%2C%26quot%3B%20AEPC%20secretary%20general%20Mithileshwar%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20tank%20Global%20Trade%20Research%20Initiative%20(GTRI)%20founder%20Ajay%20Srivastava%20said%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20this%20facility%20is%20expected%20to%20disrupt%20Bangladesh's%20export%20and%20import%20logistics%2C%20which%20depend%20on%20Indian%20infrastructure%20for%20third-country%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20previous%20mechanism%20offered%20a%20streamlined%20route%20through%20India%2C%20cutting%20transit%20time%20and%20cost.%20Now%2C%20without%20it%2C%20Bangladeshi%20exporters%20may%20face%20logistical%20delays%2C%20higher%20costs%2C%20and%20uncertainty.%20Additionally%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Bhutan%2C%20both%20landlocked%20nations%2C%20may%20raise%20concerns%20about%20restricted%20transit%20access%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20especially%20as%20this%20move%20will%20hamper%20their%20trade%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Srivastava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Bangladesh's%20plans%20for%20creating%20a%20strategic%20base%20near%20the%20Chicken's%20Neck%20area%20with%20China's%20help%20may%20have%20prompted%20this%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20always%20supported%20Bangladesh's%20cause%2C%20as%20it%20allowed%20one-way%20zero%20tariff%20access%20to%20Bangladesh%20goods%20(all%20except%20alcohol%20and%20cigarettes)%20to%20the%20vast%20Indian%20market%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India-Bangladesh%20relations%20nosedived%20dramatically%20after%20the%20interim%20government%20headed%20by%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20failed%20to%20contain%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Hindus%2C%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia-Bangladesh%20trade%20stood%20at%20%2412.9%20billion%20in%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744207920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fojkbb1pc_port-generic_625x300_09_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-terminates-trans-shipment-facility-for-bangladesh-to-export-goods-to-third-countries-8125128%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20terminated%20the%20trans-shipment%20facility%20that%20allowed%20export%20cargo%20from%20Bangladesh%20to%20third%20countries%20using%20Indian%20land%20customs%20stations%20en%20route%20to%20ports%20and%20airports%2C%20according%20to%20a%20government%20circular.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagem