s%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETamannaah%20Bhatia%20is%20set%20to%20dazzle%20in%20a%20special%20song%20for%20Raid%202%2C%20starring%20Ajay%20Devgn.%20Leaked%20footage%20from%20the%20shoot%20shows%20her%20in%20a%20white-and-gold%20outfit%2C%20sparking%20fan%20excitement.%20Known%20for%20hit%20dance%20numbers%2C%20Tamannaah%20adds%20glamour%20to%20the%20sequel%2C%20which%20releases%20on%20May%201%20with%20a%20fresh%20storyline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20US-China%20Tariff%20War%20Math%20As%20Trump%20And%20Xi%20Go%20'All-In'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20largest%20economies%20in%20the%20world%20-%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20-%20are%20at%20war%2C%20with%20tariffs%20being%20used%20by%20either%20side%20as%20its%20weapon.%20While%20the%20US%20has%20increased%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20goods%20from%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20April%201%2C%20to%20104%20per%20cent%20today%3B%20China%20has%20retaliated%20by%20upping%20tariffs%20on%20all%20American%20goods%20from%2067%20per%20cent%20on%20April%203%20to%20151%20per%20cent%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20still%20unsettled%20by%20the%20crash%20of%20the%20global%20stock%20markets%20-%20where%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20were%20wiped%20out%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%20is%20sensing%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20Fears%20of%20a%20worldwide%20recession%20arising%20from%20this%20tit-for-tat%20battle%20seem%20to%20be%20heading%20towards%20becoming%20a%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'NO-LIMITS'%20POKER%20DUEL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20two%20major%20economies%20clash%20with%20each%20other%2C%20dealing%20blow%20after%20blow%2C%20both%20leaders%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20staring%20contest%20-%20with%20neither%20willing%20to%20blink.%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20determined%20to%20teach%20%26quot%3Btariff%20abuser%26quot%3B%20China%20a%20bitter%20lesson%2C%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20said%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20to%20the%20very%20end%26quot%3B%20over%20what%20his%20country%20has%20described%20as%20American%20%26quot%3Bblackmail%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20off%20as%20a%20reciprocal%20tariff%20move%20by%20Trump%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20no-limits%20poker%20duel.%20While%20the%20US%20President%20raised%20tariffs%20on%20China%20on%20April%202nd%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%2C%20Beijing%20matched%20Washington's%20move%2C%20over%20and%20above%20its%20old%20tariffs%2C%20infuriating%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20then%20sent%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20and%20gave%20him%2024%20hours%20to%20%26quot%3Bwithdraw%26quot%3B%20his%20move.%20China's%20Xi%20decided%20to%20'check'%2C%20standing%20his%20ground%2C%20hoping%20to%20call%20Trump's%20'bluff'.%20But%20Trump%20followed%20through%20by%20'raising'%20tariffs%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20Jinping%2C%20now%20'committed'%20to%20the%20high-stakes%20battle%2C%20'matched'%20Donald%20Trump%20yet%20again%20in%20terms%20of%20reciprocity%20of%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20-%20resulting%20in%20China%20exceeding%20US'%20104%20per%20cent%20to%20reach%20151%20per%20cent%2C%20leaving%20President%20Trump%20to%20make%20his%20next%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS'%20104%25%20vs%20CHINA'S%20151%25%20-%20THE%20TARIFF%20MATH%20SO%20FAR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20both%20Trump%20and%20Xi%20well%20on%20their%20way%20to%20go%20'all-in'%2C%20dragging%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20into%20an%20uncertain%20economic%20future%2C%20here%20is%20a%20look%20at%20how%20the%20tariffs%20stand%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBefore%20April%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20'Liberation%20Day'%20-%20China%20used%20to%20levy%20tariffs%20on%20US%20goods%20at%2067%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20US%20used%20to%20impose%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20goods%20from%20China.%20This%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Brobbed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bripped-off%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20economy%20for%20decades.%20He%20said%20it%20is%20only%20fair%20for%20the%20US%20to%20match%20China.%20So%2C%20came%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20-%20to%20free%20American%20exporters%20of%20punitive%20duties%20by%20other%20nations%2C%20and%20help%20%26quot%3Bmake%20America%20wealthy%20again%26quot%3B.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Till%20now%20China's%2067%20per%20cent%20vs%20America's%2010%20per%20cent)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20April%202nd%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Donald%20Trump%20announces%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20on%20all%20nations%20that%20tariff%20American%20goods.%20This%20includes%20China%2C%20who%20he%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btariff%20abuser%20for%20decades%26quot%3B.%20Trump%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20term%20suggests%2C%20today's%20tariffs%20are%20just%20reciprocal%20-%20which%20means%20-%20we%20do%20to%20them%2C%20what%20they%20do%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%20But%20he%20added%20that%20the%20US%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bkinder%26quot%3B%20by%20charging%20roughly%20half%20of%20what%20the%20rival%20nation%20charges.%20So%2C%20for%20China%2C%20which%20charged%2067%20per%20cent%20at%20that%20time%2C%20Trump%20announced%20a%2034%20per%20cent%20hike%20in%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Till%20now%20China%20stood%20at%2067%20per%20cent%20vs%20America's%2010%2B34%2C%20equaling%2044%20per%20cent)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELater%2C%20on%20April%202nd%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Shortly%20after%20Trump's%20announcement%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20US%20will%20be%20charging%20all%20nations%20in%20the%20world%20a%20non-reciprocal%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff.%20The%20statement%20said%20that%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20emergency%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20stemmed%20from%20security%20concerns%20due%20to%20persistent%20trade%20deficits%2C%20the%20US%20will%20now%20be%20imposing%20a%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20all%20countries.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(China's%20basket%20of%20tariffs%20now%20stood%20at%2044%2B10%20%3D%2054%20per%20cent.%20While%20China's%20tariff%20levy%20on%20the%20US%20still%20stood%20at%2067%20per%20cent)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20April%204%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Forty-eight%20hours%20after%20US's%20reciprocal%20tariff%20move%2C%20China%20retaliated.%20Beijing%20announced%20that%20Trump's%20moves%20would%20impact%20Chinese%20exports%20significantly%2C%20and%20so%2C%20to%20counter%20the%20move%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%20decided%20to%20match%20Trump's%2034%20per%20cent%20increase%2C%20infuriating%20the%20US%20President%20who%20had%20warned%20all%20nations%20not%20to%20retaliate%2C%20else%20they%20will%20suffer%20further.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(US's%20tally%20of%20Chinese%20tariffs%20now%20stood%20at%2067%2B34%20%3D%20101%20per%20cent%20vs%20China's%20tally%20of%20US%20tariffs%20remained%20at%2054%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%207th%20and%20April%208th%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%20The%20weekend%20went%20by%2C%20and%20by%20now%20the%20US-China%20trade%20war%20had%20resulted%20in%20global%20markets%20losing%20several-trillion%20dollars%20in%20investor%20wealth.%20But%20Trump%20and%20Xi%20remained%20unmoved.%20Donald%20Trump%20issued%20a%2024-hour%20ultimatum%20to%20Xi%20Jinping%20to%20%26quot%3Bwithdraw%26quot%3B%20its%20retaliatory%2034%20per%20cent%20tariff%2C%20or%20face%20%26quot%3Ban%20additional%2050%20per%20cent%20tariff%26quot%3B%20on%20all%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20starting%20April%209.%20President%20Xi%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20till%20the%20end%26quot%3B%20and%20stood%20his%20ground%2C%20so%20President%20Trump%20followed-through%2024-hours%20after%20his%20threat.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(US'%20tariffs%20on%20China%20now%20stood%20at%2054%2B50%20%3D%20104%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20China's%20tariffs%20on%20US%20stood%20at%20101%20per%20cent)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%209%2C%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Vowing%20not%20to%20give%20in%20to%20American%20%26quot%3Bblackmail%26quot%3B%2C%20Beijing%20decided%20to%20further%20retaliate%20US%20tariffs%20by%20again%20matching%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Badditional%2050%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20move.%20This%20raised%20China's%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20from%2034%20per%20cent%20to%2084%20per%20cent.%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(So%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20US%20tariffs%20on%20China%20stand%20at%20104%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20Chinese%20tariffs%20on%20US%20stand%20at%20'101%2B50'%20or%20'67%2B84'%20-%20either%20way%20making%20it%20151%20per%20cent)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20war%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20has%20surged%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week%20and%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20dying%20down.%20Economists%20have%20warned%20of%20a%20possible%20recession%20in%20the%20making%2C%20as%20stock%20markets%2C%20oil%20prices%2C%20trade%2C%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20logistics%20have%20taken%20a%20massive%20hit.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744207680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fc1lbl7f4_donald-trump-xi-jinping-us-china-tariff-war_625x300_09_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-the-us-china-tariff-war-math-as-trump-and-xi-go-all-in-8126085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20largest%20economies%20in%20the%20world%20-%20US%20and%20China%20-%20are%20at%20war%2C%20with%20tariffs%20being%20used%20as%20their%20weapon.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20US%20tariffs%20on%20China%20stand%20at%20104%20per%20cent%20and%20Chinese%20tariffs%20on%20US%20stand%20at%20151%20per%20cent.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20calculation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20NGO%20'Bought'%20Girls%2C%20'Sold'%20Them%20To%20Men%20For%20Rs%205%20Lakh%2C%20Busted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20human%20trafficking%20racket%20being%20run%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20an%20NGO%20organising%20mass%20marriages%20for%20women%20from%20poor%20families%20has%20been%20busted%20near%20Jaipur.%20The%20woman%20who%20ran%20the%20NGO%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20would%20'buy'%20girls%20from%20agents%20trafficking%20them%20from%20poor%20families%20and%20'sell'%20them%20to%20young%20men%20looking%20for%20a%20bride%20for%20Rs%202.5-5%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20Gayatri%20Sarva%20Samaj%20Foundation%20had%20set%20up%20its%20office%20in%20a%20farmhouse%20in%20Sujanpura%20village%20of%20Bassi%2C%20about%2030%20km%20from%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20claimed%20to%20organise%20mass%20marriages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20a%20gang%20would%20'buy'%20girls%20from%20poor%20families%20from%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20'sell'%20them%20to%20Gayatri%20Vishwakarma%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20'NGO'.%20Gayatri%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20would%20'sell'%20these%20girls%20to%20young%20men%20who%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%20for%20Rs%202.5-5%20lakh%2C%20said%20Bassi%20police%20station%20in-charge%20Abhijit%20Patil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'price'%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20was%20decided%20according%20to%20the%20girls'%20complexion%2C%20height%20and%20age.%20Gayatri%20would%20arrange%20fake%20Aadhaar%20cards%20for%20the%20minors%20to%20show%20that%20their%20age%20was%20over%2018.%20She%20had%20arranged%20about%201%2C500%20such%20marriages%20and%20had%20ten%20cases%20against%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGirl%20Escapes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20racket%20was%20exposed%20when%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%2C%20who%20was%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20escaped%20from%20the%20farmhouse%20on%20Sunday%20and%20approached%20the%20police.%20Based%20on%20the%20girl's%20statement%2C%20the%20police%20raided%20the%20farmhouse%20and%20arrested%20Gayatri%2C%20her%20associate%20Hanuman%2C%20and%20two%20others%20-%20identified%20as%20Bhagwan%20Das%20and%20Mahendra%20-%20who%20had%20gone%20there%20to%20'buy'%20the%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20said%20all%20they%20knew%20about%20the%20'NGO'%20was%20that%20it%20arranged%20marriages%20for%20girls%20from%20poor%20families%20and%20did%20not%20have%20more%20information%20because%20the%20farmhouse%20was%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20village.%20They%20said%20another%20girl%20had%20escaped%20four%20months%20ago%20and%20tried%20to%20tell%20them%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20but%20they%20could%20not%20understand%20the%20language%20she%20was%20conversing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Somu%20Anand)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744207200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fg45982f8_rajasthan-ngo-trafficking_625x300_09_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjaipur-bassi-rajasthan-ngo-bought-girls-sold-them-to-men-for-rs-5-lakh-busted-8126025%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20human%20trafficking%20racket%20being%20run%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20an%20NGO%20organising%20mass%20marriages%20for%20women%20from%20poor%20families%20been%20busted%20near%20Jaipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20Andrew%20accuser%20leaves%20hospital%20after%20saying%20she%20had%20'four%20days%20to%20live'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744207200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2