pan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20time%20consuming.%20I%20wasn't%20ready%20to%20jump%20in%20all%20the%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20an%20experiment%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustle-pet-sitting-dog-walking-fun-flexible-easy-work-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecome%20a%20dog%20sitter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Our%20house%20and%20lives%20were%20already%20set%20up%20to%20host%20dogs%2C%20and%20this%20plan%20allowed%20me%20to%20sit%20in%20my%20indecisiveness%20for%20a%20little%20while%20longer.%20Even%20better%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20dog%20being%20a%20cash%20outflow%2C%20the%20dogs%20would%20be%20a%20cash%20inflow.%20I%20set%20up%20a%20profile%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frover-side-hustle-pet-sitting-diversify-income-after-layoff-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERover%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20website%20that%20matches%20dog%20owners%20to%20dog%20sitters%20and%20dog%20walkers%2C%20and%20declared%20myself%20open%20for%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8c71349-3550-4e9f-ad06-d4ca5fff3fc1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20is%20steady%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-we-made-five-figures-rover-side-hustle-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERover%20profile%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20highlighted%20that%20I%20was%20an%20experienced%20dog%20owner%20with%20two%20school-age%20kids.%20I%20said%20clearly%20that%20I%20would%20only%20take%20one%20dog%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20that%20dog%20would%20be%20part%20of%20the%20family%20during%20their%20stay.%20I%20stated%20that%20visiting%20pups%20get%20two%20short%20walks%20every%20day%20and%20a%20longer%20walk%20every%20few%20days%2C%20as%20well%20as%20frequent%20potty%20breaks%20in%20my%20small%2C%20fenced%20backyard.%20I%20opted%20to%20be%20little%20bit%20picky%20about%20the%20types%20of%20dogs%20I%20would%20care%20for.%20I%20prefer%20medium%20and%20large%20dogs%20that%20are%20over%20a%20year%20old%20who%20have%20been%20spayed%20or%20neutered%2C%20are%20good%20with%20kids%2C%20and%20are%20crate-trained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20starting%20in%20January%2C%20I've%20been%20busy.%20I%20haven't%20had%20a%20full%20week%20without%20a%20dog%20guest%20in%20the%20last%20four%20months.%20I'm%20currently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-dogs-hikes-upstate-service-group-walks-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echarging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%2450%20to%2065%20a%20day%2C%20which%20a%20steal%20in%20the%20area%20I%20live%20in.%20I'm%20easily%20bringing%20in%20%24600%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20and%20in%20February%2C%20when%20dogs%20came%20over%20a%20holiday%20week%20that%20qualified%20for%20my%20higher%20prices%2C%20it%20was%20nearly%20%241%2C000%2C%20even%20after%20Rover%20took%20its%2020%25%20cut.%20For%20me%2C%20that%20has%20meant%20guilt-free%20indulgences%20at%20Starbucks%20and%20a%20mini-shopping%20spree%20at%20Athleta's%20spring%20sale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad87adc3-a297-4ecd-9af0-0fae30789df6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20getting%20more%20than%20extra%20spending%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20the%20dogs%20have%20brought%20me%20more%20than%20just%20extra%20cash%2C%20they've%20also%20brought%20me%20so%20much%20joy.%20I'm%20a%20sucker%20for%20a%20wagging%20tail%20when%20I%20come%20in%20the%20door%20and%20their%20frequent%20mischievousness%20makes%20me%20laugh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20way%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-growing-up-with-pets-can-be-good-for-your-child-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecaring%20for%20the%20dogs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20became%20a%20family%20hobby.%20My%20kids%20have%20taken%20it%20as%20a%20group%20responsibility%20to%20make%20sure%20all%20our%20dog%20guests%20are%20comfortable%20and%20well-loved.%20The%20pups%20are%20all%20showered%20with%20scratches%2C%20played%20with%2C%20and%20sometimes%20allowed%20to%20snatch%20leftovers%20off%20of%20my%20kids'%20plates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20each%20new%20dog%20we%20have%20that%20new-puppy%20energy%20that%20takes%20over%20the%20house%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20dog's%20age%20is.%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20their%20cute%20floppy%20ears!%20Look%20at%20how%20they%20floofy%20they%20are!%20What%20tricks%20can%20they%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20We%20enjoy%20brainstorming%20nicknames%20for%20all%20our%20guests%2C%20seeing%20whose%20room%20they'll%20choose%20to%20sleep%20in%2C%20and%20letting%20them%20lick%20our%20stinky%20feet.%20We%20love%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20recent%20morning%2C%20we%20were%20watching%20a%20dog%20we'd%20nicknamed%20Cyborg%20due%20to%20his%20one%2C%20bright-blue%20eye.%20I%20was%20up%20earlier%20than%20usual%20because%20he'd%20woken%20me%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20overlapped%20with%20my%2012-year-old%20son.%20As%20Cyborg%20whined%20and%20paced%20and%20carried%20around%20a%20single%20sock%2C%20my%20son%20and%20I%20realized%20if%20we%20all%20left%20right%20then%2C%20we'd%20have%20time%20to%20hit%20up%20the%20coffee%20shop%20for%20a%20hot%20cocoa%20before%20he%20got%20on%20the%20bus.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20won't%20pretend%20our%20walk%20through%20the%20fog%20that%20morning%20was%20a%20life-changing%20mother-son%20moment%2C%20but%20it%20was%20special%20because%20we%20don't%20get%20to%20do%20that%20every%20day.%20It%20only%20happened%20because%20we%20had%20the%20pup%20with%20us.%20Someday%20we'll%20get%20our%20forever%20dog%2C%20but%20until%20then%20we're%20all%20enjoying%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-money-side-hustles-stay-at-home-parents-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efamily%20side%20hustle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frover-dog-sitting-side-hustle-mom-makes-extra-spending-money-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744204381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f3cdfb63d72727e1995a6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frover-dog-sitting-side-hustle-mom-makes-extra-spending-money-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20family%20wasn't%20ready%20to%20get%20a%20new%20dog%20after%20ours%20died%2C%20so%20I%20leaned%20into%20dog%20sitting.%20Now%20these%20furry%20friends%20bring%20in%20money%20instead%20of%20costing%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Carolyn%20Abram)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frover-dog-sitting-side-hustle-mom-makes-extra-spending-money-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Audio%20giant%20Bose%20invests%20Rs%20173%20cr%20in%20India's%20wearables%20brand%20Noise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744204337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faudio-giant-bose-invests-rs-173-cr-in-india-s-wearables-brand-noise-125040901055_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20funding%20follows%20Bose's%20initial%20investment%20in%20Noise's%20maiden%20funding%20in%20December%202023%2C%20wherein%20Noise%20reportedly%20raised%20USD%2010%20million%20at%20a%20valuation%20of%20USD%20420%20million%20from%2