0KOA%20it%20turned%20its%20owner%2C%20financier%20and%20investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-10-26%2Fboom-in-camping-and-glamping-makes-koa-mogul-a-billionaire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOscar%20Tang%2C%20into%20a%20billionaire%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20O'Rourke%20started%20at%20KOA%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20their%20customer%20base%20was%20overwhelming%20baby%20boomers%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20traveling%20in%20RVs.%20Today%2C%20while%20the%20retirees%20have%20stuck%20around%2C%20younger%20generations%20are%20making%20up%20a%20greater%20share%20and%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20%26quot%3Bglamping%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20more%20elevated%20camping%20experiences%20with%20unique%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKOA%20also%20found%20that%2072%25%20of%20campers%20consider%20it%20a%20cost-effective%20travel%20option%2C%20and%20O'Rourke%20said%20they%20continue%20to%20make%20it%20work%20even%20when%20facing%20economic%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20see%20high%20value%20in%20stays%20at%20campgrounds%20over%20how%20far%20their%20dollar%20goes%20at%20a%20resort%20or%20hotels%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20camp%20closer%20to%20home%2C%20or%20they're%20going%20to%20take%20a%20shorter%20stay%20versus%20a%20longer%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bor%20they%20might%20be%20canceling%20other%20types%20of%20trips%20and%20camping%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20industry%20experts%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-demand-slowdown-economic-anxiety-summer-airlines-cruises-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etravel%20demand%20is%20softening%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20advance%20of%20a%20summer%20of%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20many%20Americans%20will%20simply%20change%20their%20plans%20rather%20than%20cancel%20a%20trip%20altogether%2C%20instead%20opting%20for%20more%20affordable%20vacations%20like%20road%20trips%20or%20national%20parks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cabins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5cce43fe8d392836284f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKOA%20is%20investing%20in%20more%20glamping%20sites%20and%20upgraded%20amenities%20at%20its%20campgrounds.%3Cp%3EKOA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c15e861a-817b-4672-a0dc-19a01806f065%5C%22%3EGlamping's%20lower%20barrier%20to%20entry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20campers%20are%20also%20fueling%20the%20rise%20in%20glamping%2C%20which%20O'Rourke%20said%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20KOA%2C%20especially%20as%20luxury%20travel%20spending%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20every%20KOA%20has%20some%20form%20of%20glamping%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglamping-in-sahara-desert-freezing-but-worth-it-morocco-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlamping%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20broad%20term%20but%20generally%20refers%20to%20a%20camping%20experience%20beyond%20the%20basics%2C%20with%20amenities%20typically%20associated%20with%20traditional%20accommodations%2C%20like%20a%20hotel.%20Glamping%20can%20refer%20to%20a%20large%2C%20fancy%20tent%20with%20a%20real%20bed%2C%20a%20tiny%20cabin%2C%20or%20something%20unique%20like%20a%20treehouse%20or%20yurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20KOA%20has%20a%20glamping%20resort%20in%20Maine%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Terramor%20Outdoor%20Resort%2C%20near%20Acadia%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%94%20with%2064%20canvas%20tents%20featuring%20electricity%20and%20wifi%2C%20a%20portable%20heater%2C%20and%20a%20noise%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20KOA%20added%2015%20new%20campgrounds%20last%20year%2C%20O'Rourke%20said%20the%20company%20is%20focused%20on%20upgrading%20existing%20locations%20with%20more%20glamping%20or%20specialty%20patio%20sites%20for%20RVs.%20She%20said%20she's%20always%20focused%20on%20addressing%20pain%20points%20or%20the%20aspects%20of%20camping%20that%20make%20it%20too%20difficult%20for%20someone%20to%20try%20for%20the%20first%20time%20or%20stick%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20time%20into%20thinking%20about%20because%20otherwise%20if%20it's%20difficult%2C%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20continue%20to%20modernize%20our%20parks%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20and%20expectations%20of%20the%20current%20camper%20and%20the%20changing%20camper%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-camping-glamping-koa-recession-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744201802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5d156a466d2b74ab29e46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-camping-glamping-koa-recession-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Z%20is%20embracing%20camping%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0though%20they%20tend%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20more%20upscale%20version%20of%20the%20pastime%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20president%20of%20KOA%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-camping-glamping-koa-recession-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Vin%20Diesel%20talked%20about%20%E2%80%98steamy%E2%80%99%20chemistry%20with%20DP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744201802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120128142%2Cimgsize-94710.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%