uffers%20from%20multiple%20ailments%2C%20including%20abdominal%20aortic%20aneurysm%20at%20immediate%20risk%20of%20rupture%2C%20Parkinson's%20disease%20with%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20and%20a%20mass%20suggestive%20of%20bladder%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrop.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fimages%2Fvod%2Fmedium%2F2012-11%2Fbig_254537_1352695645.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Has%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Done%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20NIA%20chargesheet%2C%20David%20Headley%20travelled%20to%20several%20Indian%20cities%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Pushkar%2C%20Goa%20and%20Pune%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20representative%20with%20a%20company%2C%20Immigrant%20Law%20Centre.%20The%20company's%20office%20was%20located%20at%20Mumbai's%20Tardeo%20Road%20and%20it%20is%20alleged%20that%20Rana%20helped%20Headley%20set%20up%20the%20office.%20Tahawwur%20too%20travelled%20to%20different%20places%20in%20India%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%20The%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20Headley%2C%20Rana%2C%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20founder%20Hafiz%20Saeed%2C%20LeT%20co-founder%20Zaki-ur-Rehman%20Lakhvi%20and%20others%20%26quot%3Baided%20and%20abetted%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20which%20166%20persons%20were%20killed%20and%20many%20seriously%20injured%26quot%3B.%20Headley%20and%20Rana%20also%20made%20preparations%20for%20attacks%20in%20different%20places%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20Chabad%20houses%20located%20in%20different%20states%20of%20India%20and%20the%20National%20Defence%20College%2C%20Delhi%2C%20the%20chargesheeet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Was%20Rana%20Arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20David%20Headley%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20FBI%20on%20October%203%2C%202009%2C%20at%20O'Hare%20airport%20in%20Chicago.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20revelation%20made%20by%20Headley%2C%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20custody.%20On%2027th%20October%2C%202009%20the%20FBI%20filed%20criminal%20complaints%20in%20the%20District%20Court%20of%20Northern%20District%20of%20Illinois%20against%20Headley%20and%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20planning%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20foreign%20lands%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20Headley%20and%20Rana%20were%20also%20charged%20in%20the%20criminal%20conspiracy%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20The%20chargesheet%20notes%20that%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20attack%20spots%20in%20India%20was%20hatched%20in%20Pakistan.%20Seven%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20accused%2C%20except%20Headley%20and%20Rana%2C%20are%20in%20Pakistan.%20The%20chargesheet%20says%20Rana%20provided%20logistic%2C%20financial%20and%20other%20assistance%20to%20David%20Headley%20and%20the%20other%20co-conspirators%20towards%20fulfillment%20of%20the%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20organise%20terror%20attacks%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fuofsqds8_mumbai-terror-attack_625x300_25_November_18.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharges%20Against%20Rana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20says%20Rana%20assisted%20Headley%20in%20several%20ways%2C%20including%20setting%20up%20the%20Immigrant%20Law%20Centre%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20a%20front%20organisation%20to%20cover%20their%20activities%20and%20also%20visited%20India%20in%