20Eweje.%3Cp%3EPhotography%20credit%3A%20Nadia%20Vanderhall%2C%20Felicia%20Sneddon%2C%20Afolabi%20Mosuro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20new%20tariff%20policies%20have%20caused%20a%20market%20downturn%20and%20could%20impact%20the%20prices%20of%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20means%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20personal%20finance%20fundamentals%20are%20solid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20asked%20finance%20influencers%20for%20their%20budgeting%20advice%20amid%20the%20economic%20turbulence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20reexamining%20your%20monthly%20expenses%20in%20light%20of%20the%20market%20turmoil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-female-women-finance-influencers-creators-tiktok-youtube-instagram-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20finance%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20ready%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-tariffs-trade-war-trump-recession-stagflation-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20tariff%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20sent%20markets%20downward%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20wave%20of%20uncertainty%20for%20business%20owners%20and%20everyday%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20you%20do%3F%20We%20asked%20top%20finance%20influencers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-influencers-share-best-advice-as-tariffs-rock-market-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20share%20their%20No.%201%20pieces%20of%20advice%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20current%20economic%20climate.%20Rather%20than%20act%20on%20impulse%2C%20the%20influencers%20said%20not%20to%20panic.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20mentioned%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20a%20smart%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20budget%20is%20just%20a%20plan%20for%20how%20to%20pace%20your%20money%20for%20the%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nadia%20Vanderhall%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%20and%20LinkedIn%20influencer.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20about%20knowing%20what's%20coming%20in%2C%20what's%20going%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20key%20budgeting%20takeaways%20the%20influencers%20shared%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293d3591b-3b23-4cd3-8f2d-215b2853a379%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Budget%20to%20optimize%20a%20safety%20net%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvoid%20getting%20%26quot%3Bcaught%20with%20your%20pants%20down%26quot%3B%20by%20establishing%20a%20cushion%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20job%20loss%2C%20said%20Mal%20Baska%2C%20who%20has%2031%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20account%20Money%20Talk%20Mal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnsure%20you%20have%20a%20solid%20cash%20cushion%2C%20or%20emergency%20fund%2C%20in%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20Baska%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20not%2C%20budget%20to%20optimize%20this%20cushion%20and%20safety%20net.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTuber%20Sebastian%20Fung%2C%20whose%20AskSebby%20account%20has%20312%2C000%20subscribers%2C%20recommends%20having%206%20to%2012%20months%20of%20expenses%20in%20savings%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20are%20concerned%20about%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20look%20into%20money%20market%20funds%20or%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20%E2%80%94%20that%20way%2C%20you're%20still%20earning%20interest%20while%20maintaining%20liquidity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dd25725-9d65-43a2-a5f5-451e4be061fc%5C%22%3E2.%20How%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20prices%20begin%20to%20go%20up%2C%20Vanderhall%20said%20to%20look%20at%20your%20last%20month's%20spending%20to%20see%20what%20expenses%20have%20increased%20and%20use%20that%20information%20to%20shape%20your%20budget%20for%20the%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanderhall%20said%20to%20start%20with%20real%20numbers%3A%20Look%20at%20your%20actual%20income%20and%20expenses%20by%20analyzing%20your%20bank%20and%20credit%20card%20statements%20from%20the%20last%2030%20to%2060%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreak%20your%20budget%20down%20into%20categories%20such%20as%20bills%2C%20groceries%2C%20transportation%2C%20debt%2C%20savings%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bfun%26quot%3B%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20ways%20to%20track%20a%20budget%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20use%20a%20method%20that%20matches%20your%20lifestyle%2C%20Vanderhall%20said.%20That%20could%20be%20writing%20it%20down%2C%20using%20a%20spreadsheet%2C%20or%20using%20an%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETolani%20Eweje%2C%20who%20writes%20the%20Substack%20newsletter%20The%20Creator%20Success%20Club%2C%20said%20simple%20budgets%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20this%20framework%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E50%25%20essentials%20(bills%2C%20housing%2C%20groceries%2C%20etc.)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E30%25%20wants%20(travel%2C%20dining%20out%2C%20etc.)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E20%25%20future%20(savings%2C%20investments)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20income%20fluctuates%20month-to-month%2C%20base%20it%20on%20your%20last%20six%20months'%20average%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221555de1d-0f1c-48c3-98f4-a9194afd4265%5C%22%3E3.%20Negotiate%20recurring%20bills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20evaluated%20your%20budget%2C%20go%20a%20step%20further%20by%20trying%20to%20lower%20your%20costs.%20Baska%20said%20you%20should%20start%20soon%20if%20you%20are%20worried%20about%20price%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNegotiate%20your%20auto%20insurance%2C%20cellphone%2C%20medical%20bills%2C%20salary%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20Baska%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20lock%20in%20pricing%20before%20companies%20really%20get%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20salary%2C%20take%20the%20time%20to%20learn%20your%20state's%20salary%20history%20and%20transparency%20laws%2C%20said%20Hannah%20Williams%2C%20creator%20of%20Salary%20Transparent%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20knowing%20your%20market%20rate%20and%20legal%20protections%20leaves%20you%20vulnerable%20to%20being%20underpaid%20and%20taken%20advantage%20of%20by%20employers%20looking%20to%20save%20on%20their%20bottom%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22deb12497-6721-401f-b30c-77ceafa81e63%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Sick%20of%20spreadsheets%3F%20Use%20a%20budgeting%20app%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20more%20of%20a%20spreadsheet%20person%2C%20you%20can%20build%20your%20own%20budget%20sheet%20using%20Google%20Sheets%20or%20Excel%2C%20said%20Bola%20Sokunbi%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20Clever%20Girl%20Finance%20with%20356%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you're%20more%20into%20apps%2C%20the%20best%20one%20is%20the%20one%20you'll%20actually%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokunbi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommends%20browsing%20the%20top-reviewed%20budgeting%20apps%20in%20your%20phone's%20app%20store%20and%20testing%20a%20few%20out%20until%20you%20find%20one%20that%20fits%20your%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20influencers%20recommended%20several%20apps%2C%20including%20Lunch%20Money%2C%20Monarch%20Money%2C%20Copilot%20Money%2C%20Origin%20Financial%2C%20and%20tMoney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSetting%20realistic%20budget%20parameters%20and%20spending%20categories%20is%20key%20to%20success%20and%20sustainability%2C%26quot%3B%20Baska%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e7fda09-baeb-4005-a8a7-51e187c20b2f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Evaluate%20your%20budget%20weekly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20evaluating%20your%20finances%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20month%2C%20Fung%20recommends%20doing%20it%20weekly%20so%20that%20you%20can%20adjust%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20way%20if%20you%20spent%20too%20much%20money%20eating%20out%2C%20you%20can%20plan%20to%20cook%20the%20following%20week%2C%20Fung%20said.%20That's%20especiall