%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOnly%20When%20We%20Summon...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20Emergency%20Aid%20In%20Road%20Accident%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20reprimanded%20the%20centre%20for%20failing%20to%20implement%20a%20cashless%20medical%20treatment%20plan%20that%20includes%20access%20to%20emergency%20aid%20during%20the%20'golden%20hour'%20-%20i.e.%2C%20the%20critical%20first%2060%20minutes%20after%20a%20person%20suffers%20severe%20trauma%20-%20for%20road%20accident%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20ordered%20the%20cashless%20treatment%20scheme%20be%20implemented%20by%20March%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTime%20granted%20to%20the%20government%20expired%20on%20March%2014...%20this%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20breach%20and%20violation%20of%20an%20order%20of%20this%20court%20and%20failure%20to%20implement%20a%20very%20beneficial%20provision...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Ministry%2C%20were%20summoned%20by%20an%20irate%20top%20court.%20They%20are%20to%20appear%20on%20April%2028%20to%20%26quot%3Bexplain%20the%20default...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20our%20long%20experience...%20only%20when%20we%20get%20top%20government%20officials%20here%20do%20they%20take%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20court%20seriously.%20Otherwise%20they%20won't%20take%20it...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20making%20it%20very%20clear...%20we%20will%20issue%20notice%20of%20contempt%20if%20we%20find%20that%20no%20progress%20is%20made.%20People%20are%20losing%20their%20lives%20because%20there%20is%20no%20treatment...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20centre%20to%20immediately%20frame%20a%20scheme%20for%20emergency%20medical%20aid%20for%20road%20accident%20survivors%2C%20particularly%20in%20'golden%20hour'%20cases%20and%20in%20those%20where%20family%20or%20close%20friends%20may%20not%20be%20available%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20life-saving%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Oka%20noted%20that%20bystanders%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20even%20the%20hospitals%20sometimes%20wait%20for%20the%20other%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%2C%20particularly%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20treatment%20costs%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20This%20practice%2C%20the%20court%2C%20said%20puts%20people's%20lives%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20Section%20162(2)%20of%20the%20amended%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%20included%20a%20mandate%20to%20insurance%20companies%20to%20provide%20cashless%20emergency%20medical%20treatment%20of%20road%20accident%20survivors%2C%20and%20noted%20that%20this%20had%20not%20been%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlans%20for%20cashless%20medical%20treatment%20for%20road%20accident%20survivors%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20'golden%20hour'%20had%20first%20been%20floated%20by%20the%20centre%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744192200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmhuvv8ko_dholpur-road-accident_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-cashless-medical-treatment-golden-hour-road-accidents-8124073%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20reprimanded%20the%20centre%20for%20failing%20to%20implement%20a%20cashless%20medical%20treatment%20plan%20that%20includes%20access%20to%20emergency%20aid%20during%20the%20'golden%20hour'%20for%20road%20accident%20survivors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-cashless-medical-treatment-golden-hour-road-accidents-8124073%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%