ot%20Unique%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20we%20going%20to%20be%20happy%20being%20delivery%20boys%20and%20girls%3F%E2%80%9D%20Commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20taunted%20the%20Indian%20startup%20industry%20at%20the%202025%20edition%20of%20Startup%20Mahakumbh%20in%20New%20Delhi%20last%20week.%20At%20the%20annual%20jamboree%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20for%20industry%20upstarts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5_f9jAvbkDU%5C%22%3EGoyal%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20What%20are%20Indian%20startups%20of%20today%20-%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20food%20delivery%20apps%2C%20turning%20unemployed%20youth%20into%20cheap%20labour%20so%20the%20rich%20can%20get%20their%20meals%20without%20moving%20out%20of%20their%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20typical%20Indian%20middle-class%20parents%20comparing%20the%20marksheet%20of%20the%20neighbour's%20child%20with%20that%20of%20their%20own%2C%20Goyal%20did%20the%20inevitable%20side-by-side%20comparison%20with%20Chinese%20startups.%20Highlighting%20the%20stark%20contrast%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20while%20Chinese%20companies%20developed%20electric%20mobility%20and%20mobility%20tech%2C%20Indian%20startups%20were%20focused%20on%20food%20delivery%20and%20gig%20work.%20That%20won't%20do%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20the%20sculptors%20of%20new%20India.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20Viksit%20Bharat%202047%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal's%20lament%20predictably%20got%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20startup%20industry%2C%20with%20some%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20minister%20got%20his%20numbers%20wrong%2C%20and%20others%20asking%20him%20to%20also%20compare%20the%20regulatory%20and%20policy%20framework%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20for%20good%20measure.%20While%20Goyal%20is%20not%20entirely%20wrong%20about%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20innovation%20in%20the%20Indian%20industry%2C%20where%20is%20he%20really%20coming%20from%3F%20Why%20the%20deeptech%20%E2%80%98FOMO'%3F%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20dramatic%20arrival%20of%20commercially%20viable%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20suddenly%20revealed%20the%20disturbing%20possibility%20of%20a%20world%20divided%20into%20AI%20haves%20and%20have-nots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20deeper%20worry%2C%20unstated%20in%20the%20speech%2C%20at%20work.%20It%20is%20the%20foreboding%20of%20an%20impending%20war%20and%20the%20feeling%20of%20unpreparedness.%20The%20surge%20of%20nationalism%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20retreat%20of%20democracy%20across%20the%20world%2C%20accentuates%20it.%20Goyal%20is%20not%20alone.%20The%20fear%20is%20global%2C%20and%20nationalist%20leaders%20want%20private%20entrepreneurs%20to%20feel%20and%20share%20it.%20But%20each%20has%20a%20different%20approach.%20While%20China%20wants%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20be%20under%20the%20party's%20thumb%2C%20Europe%20wants%20to%20handle%20the%20private%20sector%20with%20kid%20gloves.%20The%20US%20industry%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20seeking%20the%20unleash-the-crazy-billionaire%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20February%20Meeting%20In%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20cracking%20down%20on%20the%20private%20sector%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Chinese%20leadership%20sat%20down%20with%20business%20leaders%20and%20entrepreneurs%20in%20February.%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20told%20them%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20policies%20and%20guidelines%20of%20the%20(Chinese%20Communist)%20Party%20and%20the%20state%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20private%20economy%20have%20been%20incorporated%20into%20the%20system%20of%20socialism%20with%20Chinese%20characteristics%2C%20and%20will%20be%20adhered%20to%20and%20implemented%20consistently.%20They%20cannot%20and%20will%20not%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20urged%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20completely%20align%20with%20the%20objectives%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20for%20high-quality%20growth%20and%20national%20goals.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20time%20for%20private%20enterprises%20and%20private%20entrepreneurs%20to%20show%20their%20talents.%E2%80%9D%20Manoj%20Kewalramani%2C%20who%20heads%20China%20research%20at%20Takshashila%20Institution%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrackingpeoplesdaily.substack.com%2Fp%2Fwhats-xis-message-to-private-entrepreneurs%5C%22%3Epoints%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20choice%20of%20speakers%20indicated%20emphasis%20on%20hard%20tech%20and%20industrial%20technology%20over%20consumer%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDraghi%20Report%20In%20Europe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresenting%20the%20%3Cem%3EFuture%20of%20European%20Competitiveness%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcommission.europa.eu%2Ftopics%2Feu-competitiveness%2Fdraghi-report_en%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20European%20Parliament%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Mario%20Draghi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20core%20problem%20in%20Europe%20is%20that%20new%20companies%20with%20new%20technologies%20are%20not%20rising%20in%20our%20economy.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20is%20no%20EU%20company%20with%20a%20market%20capitalisation%20over%20%E2%82%AC100%20billion%20that%20has%20been%20set%20up%20from%20scratch%20in%20the%20last%20fifty%20years.%E2%80%9D%20Draghi%20said%20innovating%20and%20growing%20big%20tech%20companies%20was%20essential%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20European%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20European%20Union%20exists%20to%20ensure%20that%20Europe's%20fundamental%20values%20are%20always%20upheld%3A%20democracy%2C%20freedom%2C%20peace%2C%20equity%20and%20prosperity%20in%20a%20sustainable%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20imports%2080%25%20of%20its%20digital%20technology%2C%20and%20only%20four%20out%20of%20the%20world's%2050%20top%20tech%20companies%20are%20European.%20Draghi's%20answer%20to%20that%20was%20preparing%20a%20conducive%20environment%20and%20investing%20in%20the%20right%20places.%20He%20wanted%20Europe%20to%20overhaul%20its%20approach%20to%20skills%2C%20using%20data%20to%20identify%20skills%20gaps%20and%20investing%20in%20education%20at%20every%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20Europe%20to%20succeed%2C%20investment%20in%20technology%20and%20in%20people%20cannot%20substitute%20for%20each%20other.%20They%20must%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuggesting%20urgent%20regulatory%20overhaul%20to%20create%20a%20truly%20European%20single%20market%2C%20the%20Draghi%20report%20seeks%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprofound%20review%E2%80%9D%20of%20funding%20innovation%20through%20public%20money.%20Breakthrough%20technologies%20are%20often%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20risky%20or%20require%20too%20much%20financing%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20bear%2C%20it%20says%2C%20and%20bats%20for%20private%20investment%20to%20be%20reoriented%20towards%20hi-tech%20sectors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Techbros%20In%20The%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chinese%20tech's%20long%20march%20continues%20along%20Xi%20Jinping's%20doctrine%20of%20perfecting%20%E2%80%9Csocialism%20with%20Chinese%20characteristics%20for%20the%20new%20era%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20Draghi%20urges%20innovation%20in%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20preserve%20the%20European%20value%20system%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20deputy%2C%20JD%20Vance%2C%20play%20mascots%20for%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20tech%20nationalism%20driven%20by%20billionaire%20Silicon%20Valley%20tech%20bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bewildering%20ideological%20treatise%20titled%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Technological%20Republic%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20recently%20published%20by%20the%20maverick%20CEO%20of%20currently%20America's%20most%20valuable%20defence%20tech%20firm%2C%20Palantir%20Technologies.%20In%20the%20book%2C%20the%20author%2C%20Alex%20Karp%2C%20who%20co-founded%20Palantir%20with%20billionaire%20Peter%20Thiel%2C%20echoes%20Goyal's%20sentiments%20about%20consumer%20app%20companies%20and%20bemoans%20the%20decline%20of%20American%20technological%20ambition.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20market%20rewarded%20shallow%20engagement%20with%20the%20potential%20of%20technology%2C%20as%20startup%20after%20startup%20catered%20to%20the%20whims%20of%20late%20capitalist%20culture%20without%20any%20interest%20in%20constructing%20the%20technical%20infrastructure%20that%20would%20address%20our%20most%20significant%20challenges%20as%20a%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karp%20laments.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20age%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20food%20delivery%20apps%20had%20arrived.%20Medical%20breakthroughs%2C%20education%20reform%2C%20and%20military%20advances%20would%20have%20to%20wait.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarp%20and%20Thiel%20are%20among%20the%20influential%20tech%20billionaires%20and%20financiers%20backing%20Trump%20and%20Vance.%20The%20veep%2C%20once%20a%20sworn%20Trump%20baiter%2C%20virtually%20owes%20his%20political%20career%20to%20Thiel%2C%20who%20heavily%20funded%20his%20campaigns.%20Thiel%20uses%20his%20wealth%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20transform%20American%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarp's%20thesis%20could%20be%20read%20with%20his%20colleague%20and%20Palantir%20CTO%20Shyam%20Sankar's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.18theses.com%2F%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20manifesto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Defense%20Reformation%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20drastically%20changing%20the%20way%20the%20government%20approaches%20the%20defence%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20prayed%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20process%20for%20too%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sankar%20writes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20time%20to%20waste%20in%20resurrecting%20the%20American%20Industrial%20Base%20we%20depended%20on%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarp%20argues%20that%20Silicon%20Valley%20giants%20that%20dominate%20the%20American%20economy%20have%20made%20the%20strategic%20mistake%20of%20casting%20themselves%20as%20existing%20essentially%20outside%20the%20country%20in%20which%20they%20were%20built.%20They%20saw%20America%20as%20a%20dying%20empire.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20vital%20yet%20messy%20questions%20of%20what%20constitutes%20a%20good%20life%2C%20which%20collective%20endeavours%20society%20should%20pursue%2C%20and%20what%20a%20shared%20and%20national%20identity%20can%20make%20possible%2C%20have%20been%20set%20aside%20as%20the%20anachronisms%20of%20another%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20prefaces%20before%20advocating%20a%20sort%20of%20tech%20nationalism%20to%20restore%20America's%20glory%20through%20innovation%20and%20invention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20India%20Catch%20Up%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20minister%2C%20too%2C%20wants%20entrepreneurs%20to%20join%20the%20wave%20of%20nationalism%20sweeping%20through%20the%20world.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20no%20surprise%20that%20Goyal%20reserved%20high%20praise%20for%20the%20country's%20defence%20industry%2C%20which%20was%20growing%20by%20leaps%20and%20bounds.%20Yet%2C%20entrepreneurs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsIKPG2txebw%5C%22%3Eretort%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%20hardly%20offers%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20innovation.%20Far%20from%20it.%20They%20say%20whatever%20Indian%20startups%20have%20achieved%20is%20not%20because%20of%20the%20government%20but%20despite%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20proves%20their%20point%20-%20and%2C%20perversely%2C%20Goyal's%20too.%20In%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataforindia.com%2Femail%2F62354ef1-d66e-4967-830c-2485076cc721%2F%5C%22%3E97%25%20of%20Indian%20households%3C%2Fa%3E%20owned%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20but%20only%207%25%20owned%20a%20computer%20or%20laptop.%20That%20drops%20to%202%25%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Only%20two%20in%2010%20Indians%20know%20how%20to%20use%20a%20computer%2C%20but%20eight%20out%20of%2010%20can%20easily%20handle%20a%20mobile%20phone.%20ICT%20skills%20of%20youngsters%20are%20comparable%20to%20Russia%2C%20Brazil%20and%20Bangladesh%20but%20are%20way%20below%20developed%20economies%20such%20as%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%2C%20number%20crunchers%20at%20%3Cem%3EData%20for%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataforindia.com%2Fict-skills%2F%3Futm_source%3Dnewsletter%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20analysing%20government-gathered%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%2C%20as%20he%20mentioned%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20may%20be%20able%20to%20inspire%20young%20Indians%2C%20but%20he%20cannot%20skill%20them%20to%20challenge%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20'The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744184520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2qs43sco_piyush-goyal_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpiyush-goyals-deep-tech-fomo-is-not-unique-8123138%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20minister%20wants%20entrepreneurs%20to%20join%20the%20wave%20of%20nationalism%20sweeping%20through%20the%20world%2C%20across%20China%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20America.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpiyush-goyals-deep-tech-fomo-is-not-unique-8123138%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Could%20Trump's%20tariffs%20tip%20the%20world%20into%20recession%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744181940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F04%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-trump-tariffs_6880612.jpg%3F20250409090727%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcould-trumps