p%3E%3Cem%3E(Representational%20featured%20image%20courtesy%20%3C%2Fem%3EORF%20online)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20renewable%20energy%2C%20recently%20surpassing%20Japan%20to%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20generator%20of%20wind%20and%20solar%20power%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Ember.%20In%202023%2C%20solar%20energy%20accounted%20for%205.8%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20electricity%20production%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20rise%20from%20just%200.5%25%20in%202015%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20a%20major%20leap%20towards%20cleaner%20and%20more%20sustainable%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Indian%20households%2C%20this%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20national%20milestone%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20practical%20opportunity%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20rising%20electricity%20bills%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20upcoming%20peak%20summer%20months.%20By%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20panels%2C%20homeowners%20can%20generate%20their%20own%20electricity%20and%20reduce%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403520%2Fsnl-energy-solutions-provide-solar-power-to-impoverished-homes-in-rural-manipur-empower-women-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20power%20grid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20government%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Suryodaya%20Yojana%2C%20the%20shift%20to%20solar%20power%20has%20become%20more%20accessible.%20The%20scheme%20offers%20subsidies%20covering%20up%20to%2060%25%20of%20installation%20costs%20and%20provides%20loan%20support%20for%20the%20remaining%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E