0approach%20offers%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20dual%20income%2C%20as%20both%20fish%20and%20plants%20can%20be%20harvested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20guide%20offers%20tips%20on%20setting%20up%20a%20commercial%20aquaponics%20farm%2C%20covering%20crucial%20aspects%20such%20as%20setup%20processes%2C%20costs%2C%20fertilisation%2C%20pH%20and%20temperature%20management%2C%20and%20water%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20How%20much%20space%20do%20you%20need%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kerala-based%20farmer%20Vijayakumar%20Narayanan%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299137%2Fkerala-farmer-aquaponics-farming-fish-vegetables-earns-in-lakhs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CTo%2520put%2520together%2520an%2520aquaponics%2Cchoice%252C%2520especially%2520for%2520a%2520beginner.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaquaponics%20farm%20can%20be%20set%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20less%20than%20900%20sq%20ft%20of%20land.%20Ideally%2C%20half%20the%20space%20should%20be%20dedicated%20to%20a%20fish%20pond%20and%20the%20other%20half%20to%20crops.%20This%20setup%20can%20support%20up%20to%20two%20tonnes%20of%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20What%20does%20the%20setup%20include%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncorporate%20components%20such%20as%20fish%20tanks%2C%20NFT%20pipes%20(Nutrient%20Film%20Technique)%2C%20water%20pumps%2C%20and%20bio-filters.%20Delhi-based%20Peter%20Singh%2C%20an%20aquaponics%20expert%20who%20has%20built%20a%20green%20oasis%20to%20fight%20air%20pollution%2C%20recommends%20designing%20a%20system%20where%20water%20from%20the%20fish%20tank%20circ